&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Provide subject matter expertise to realistically represent the African Union (AU) and/or Economic Community of the Wes

