&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assessment of new cyber security products or technologies. This will involve researching the product, liaising with the manufacturer, arranging for a lab trial, conducting a test phase and then writing a report and making recommendations to NSPA.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implementation of new secure solutions for various projects and to ensure that NSPA Cyber Security posture remains adequate and aligned with best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating effectiveness testing and improvement of existing cyber security controls involving various cyber security technologies (including but not limited to network firewalls, Web Application firewalls, SIEM, Network IPS, e-mail protection, web browsing protection, Public Key Infrastructure, Medium and Strong authentication, etc.).&lt;/li&gt;
